The paper focuses on the automatic generation of facial images using GANs, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also address the issue of dataset quality and model stability, which are common concerns in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper specifically deals with anime characters, which falls under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
